    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gear up and <i>attack aggressively</i> with all new Contra-themed cosmetics!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock an exclusive Supreme tier skin for Jaguar ~ the Bill Rizer hero skin, complete with original voice lines and a hero item reskin. This pack also includes two Contra splats and an additional 500 X8 coins to spend in the in-game shop. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >**Disclaimer: This pack does <strong>not</strong> include the <strong><i>X8 Contra: Super Wall Storm</i></strong> game mode (sold separately).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The following content is included: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“Bill Rizer” Jaguar hero skin</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“Pixel Bill” splat tag</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“Bill Dap” splat tag</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >500 X8 Coins</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once downloaded, you can access and equip the hero skin and splat tags from the in-game Vault in the shop area. The <strong>Bill Rizer</strong> skin can be found under the <strong>Hero Skins &gt; Jaguar</strong> tab.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The purchase of X8 is required to use this add-on.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224200/extras/3d7f76ac6d0eb9b36185e3bb6ac1dc5c.avif?t=1734025906\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224200/extras_big/3d7f76ac6d0eb9b36185e3bb6ac1dc5c.avif?t=1734025906 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
